### Markdown Document Display
* Learn the Markdown Design Pattern
* Use one PHP file to display different documents


### Query Parameter
* Data can be passed within the URL

```
index.php

index.php?name=Mark

index.php?name=Mark&doc=big_book
```


### Query Parameter
* Data can be passed within the URL

```
<a href="index.php">Welcome no one</a><

<a href="index.php?name=Mark.Seaman">Welcome Mark</a>
```


### Passing Data to View
* filter_input gets values from variables
* INPUT_GET is the variable for the URL
* name is the parameter we want

```php
    $name = filter_input(INPUT_GET, 'name');
```


### Passing Data to View
* Set a default value when no value passed

```php
    // Extract the name from the URL
    $name = filter_input(INPUT_GET, 'name');
    if (!$name) {
        $name = 'No Name';
    }
```


